html"><em>《最终幻想 VII：第一士兵》</em></a>的开发商。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>另外两名前工人佐佐木大辅（Taisuke Sasaki）和铃木文明（Fumiaki Suzuki）也因购买爱明股份而被捕。 Square Enix 此前表示，正在与调查人员合作，并已制定保障措施来防止内幕交易。</p><p>这种活动在技术领域<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/opensea-nft-insider-trading-184637250.html">并不新鲜</a>。然而，这在游戏界很少见。当它涉及像 Naka 这样的成功开发人员时，令人惊讶。虽然这不一定会损害索尼克系列，但肯定对他的声誉没有帮助。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/sonic-the-hedgehog-co-creator-yuji-naka-receives-suspended-prison-sentence-for-insider-trading-173010653.html?src =rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/sonic-the-hedgehog-co-creator-yuji-naka-receives-suspended-prison-sentence-for-insider-trading-173010653.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> c063a3b7-e0ef-456f-bc67-6d0064558fed</guid><dc:creator>乔恩·芬加斯</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Fri, 07 Jul 2023 17:30:10 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1688750119</ingested><modified> 2023-07-07T17:15:22+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Investment & Company Information]]></category><category><![CDATA[Crime & Justice]]></category><category><![CDATA[Finance]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Jon Fingas]]></category><media:content height="5464" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2022-10/6d52cdc0-44a1-11ed-bfde-c7364b295ff0" width="8095"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="5464" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue