/div><p>至于其他附加功能，无线扬声器每次充电可使用 30 小时，并具有快速充电功能。这些是支持蓝牙的扬声器，因此您无需与电视绑定，而电视是家庭影院设置的传统方式。</p><p>索尼的 HT-AX7 家庭影院系统售价 500 美元， <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Sony;elmt:;cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=15919d69-aefa-41ae-a977-fdcae58a803c&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Sony&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAVsYZ8EVuWi_l1j5TbuyroCI1u0hRYKATc4wFTWTJunZ&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Felectronics.sony.com%2Faudio%2Fspeakers%2Fall-speakers%2Fp%2Fhtax7" class="rapid-with-clickid"><ins>现已开始接受预订。</ins></a>这些设备将于 7 月 18 日开始发货。如果您想<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/how-to-build-a-budget-home-theater-setup-140010399.html"><ins>构建一个预算友好的家庭影院系统，这个价格相当不错。</ins></a></p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/sonys-new-spatial-sound-system-is-actually-portable-170008725.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/sonys-new-spatial-sound-system-is-actually-portable-170008725.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> eb69cb1b-17ba-4a4a-8706-d867fd58627b</guid><dc:creator>劳伦斯·邦克</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Fri, 07 Jul 2023 17:00:08 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1688746708</ingested><modified> 2023-07-07T16:18:32+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Consumer Discretionary]]></category><category><![CDATA[Speakers & Headphones]]></category><category><![CDATA[Audio Technology]]></category><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Lawrence Bonk]]></category><media:content height="800" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-07/9ac87fe0-1cdf-11ee-bbcb-60e212380060" width="1200"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="800" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-07/9ac87fe0-1cdf-11ee-bbcb-60e212380060" width="1200"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Sony Electronics, Inc.]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[A lady in a bubble of sound created by Sony speakers.]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Sony HT-AX7 Speakers]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[The first drug that slows Alzheimer's has finally received FDA approval]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>近十年来，日本制药商卫材 (Eisai) 和美国百健 (Biogen) 一直在合作推进阿尔茨海默氏症领域的研究。最后， <a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.fda.gov/news-events/press-announcements/fda-converts-novel-alzheimers-disease-treatment-traditional-approval">FDA</a>批准了这一劳动成果 Leqembi 的静脉注射使用。这标志着第一个获得批准的可以减缓阿尔茨海默病进展的治疗方法。</p><p> Leqembi 一月份获得了初步批准，允许其在有限的范围内使用。该批准的条件是两家制药商进行验证性研究以验证该药物的临床益处。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>尽管 Leqembi 可以减缓阿尔茨默病的进展，但它并不是治愈方法。相反，它解决了促进阿尔茨海默病进展的潜在生物学问题。该<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.eisai.com/news/2023/pdf/enews202349pdf.pdf">药物的作用</a>是减少阿尔茨海默病患者大脑中形成的淀粉样斑块或“错误折叠”蛋白质。</p><p> Leqembi 并不是唯一一种针对 β-淀粉样蛋白斑块积聚来治疗阿尔茨海默病的药物。 <a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.fda.gov/drugs/postmarket-drug-safety-information-patients-and-providers/aducanumab-marketed-aduhelm-information">Aduhelm</a>于 2021 年在相同的加速途径下获得批准，但仍未完全获得 FDA 批准。但 Leqembi 与其前身的不同之处在于，除了简单地减少上述蛋白质的积累之外，该药物还证明了实际的临床益处。</p><p>服用该药物除了需要医生处方外，还需要每两周到医院或输液中心进行专业管理。尽管该公司可能不是其唯一的责任，但它认识到需要提高可访问性。 Biogen 首席执行官 Christopher Viehbacher 在一份<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://investors.biogen.com/news-releases/news-release-details/fda-grants-traditional-approval-leqembir-lecanemab-irmb">公开声明</a>中表示，该公司现在的主要重点是与卫材合作，使 Leqembi“尽快为符合条件的患者提供服务”。</p><p>不幸的是，该药物高达 26,500 美元的高昂价格让大多数人无法获得。目前的规则意味着它不太可能被医疗保险覆盖。根据<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.alz.org/alzheimers-dementia/treatments/lecanemab-leqembi">阿尔茨海默病协会的说法</a>，在大多数情况下，那些接受医疗补助的人应该能够获得 FDA 批准的药物的承保。但是，即使 Medicaid 确实承保，患者也需要支付 20% 的自付费用，即约 5,300 美元。专家预测，如果考虑到输液和实验室检查，Leqembi 治疗的总费用<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:;elmt:;cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL2xpbmsuc3ByaW5nZXIuY29tL2FydGljbGUvMTAuMTQyODMvanBhZC4yMDIzLjczIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiI5NzFjMDMyNy1jMTU2LTQ0ODctYjQ3Yi0wM2U2NTdmMzk3YzkifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAQyF69tBCmSR3ugtqJRyPOau24LH0UNVjoBEi0DttBz7&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Flink.springer.com%2Farticle%2F10.14283%2Fjpad.2023.73" class="rapid-with-clickid">每年可能高达 90,000 美元</a>。</p><p>对于 65 岁以上患有阿尔茨海默氏痴呆症的美国人来说，有九分之一的人需要考虑昂贵的治疗计划。随着国家人口老龄化的持续增长，这一数字预计还会增长。预计 65 岁及以上的美国人数量将从 2021 年的 5800 万攀升至 2050 年的 8800 万。这导致人们越来越关注阿尔茨海默氏症的治疗和诊断，例如<a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/researchers-develop-blood-test-detects-alzheimers-disease-224320271.html">可以检测该疾病的血液测试。</a></p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/the-first-drug-that-slows-alzheimers-has-finally-received-fda-approval-165058452.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/the-first-drug-that-slows-alzheimers-has-finally-received-fda-approval-165058452.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 971c0327-c156-4487-b47b-03e657f397c9</guid><dc:creator>马拉克·萨利赫</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Fri, 07 Jul 2023 16:53:03 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1688752577</ingested><modified> 2023-07-07T17:56:21+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Health Care Industry]]></category><category><![CDATA[Health]]></category><category><![CDATA[Government]]></category><category><![CDATA[Alzheimer's Disease & Dementia]]></category><category><![CDATA[Brain & Nervous System Disorders]]></category><category><![CDATA[Disease & Medical Conditions]]></category><category><![CDATA[Pharmaceuticals & Drug Trials]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Malak Saleh]]></category><media:content height="4125" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-07/de4ae590-1cdb-11ee-bceb-09710f013956" width="5500"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="3648" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-07/fd3935d0-1cd9-11ee-b7f5-b6e1834d6298" width="5472"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ASSOCIATED PRESS]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[FILE - The Biogen Inc., headquarters is shown March 11, 2020, in Cambridge, Mass. Medicare says it will limit coverage of a $28,000-a-year Alzheimer’s drug whose benefits have been widely questioned. Tuesday's decision from the Centers for Medicare and Medicaid Services is a major step in the nation’s search for ways to put a fair value on new medicines that offer tantalizing possibilities but come with prohibitive prices. It means that patients taking Biogen’s Aduhelm medication will have to be part of research efforts to assess the drug’s effectiveness in slowing the progression of dementia. The drug has sparked controversy since its approval by the Food and Drug Administration last June, which came against the recommendation of the agency’s outside advisers (AP Photo/Steven Senne, File)]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Medicare Alzheimers Drug]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Meta suspends Instagram and Threads account that tracked Elon Musk's private jet]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p> Meta 的<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/all-the-questions-we-still-have-about-threads-153059430.html">Threads</a> <a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/threads-gained-10-million-new-users-in-seven-hours-090838140.html">本周出现爆炸式增长</a>，在该应用程序<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/metas-threads-app-is-here-to-challenge-twitter-230039730.html">上线后</a>约 40 小时内<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.threads.net/t/CuZsgfWLyiI">注册了</a>超过 7000 万个帐户。其中一位用户是埃隆·马斯克(Elon Musk)熟悉的<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/how-messy-might-twitter-get-under-musk-002717320.html">眼中钉</a>，因为他们发布了这位推特所有者<a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://twitter.com/elonmusk/status/1603587970832793600">曾经称之为</a>“基本上是暗杀坐标”的内容。</p><p>然而，Meta 已在 Instagram 和 Threads 上<a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://twitter.com/Jxck_Sweeney/status/1677363511532429331">暂停了</a>@elonmusksjet。这是该账户创建者杰克·斯威尼 (Jack Sweeney) 的说法，他利用公开的飞行数据近乎实时地分享马斯克私人飞机的行踪。 Sweeney<a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://twitter.com/Jxck_Sweeney/status/1677363511532429331">在 Twitter 上写道</a>，Meta 之前就知道 Instagram 上存在该帐户（Threads 帐户<a data-i13n="cpos:9;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/meta-is-working-to-stop-deleted-threads-accounts-from-nuking-instagram-too-094423213.html">暂时与 Instagram 关联</a>），并希望此次暂停是公司的一个错误。 Engadget 已联系 Meta 了解更多详情。 </p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><div id="692f0db0448943a4aac26dae7553dfd7"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet"><p dir="ltr" lang="en">好吧，我假设人们正在线程上玩弄报告系统，但 ElonJet 只是在 IG/Threads 上暂停。 Meta 已经意识到我在该平台上安装了 ElonJet，所以我希望这是一个错误。无论如何，蓝天<a href="https://t.co/w0lnY72Rs2">pic.twitter.com/w0lnY72Rs2</a></p> — 杰克·斯威尼 (@Jxck_Sweeney) <a href="https://twitter.com/Jxck_Sweeney/status/1677363511532429331?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2023 年 7 月 7 日</a></blockquote></div><p>周五早些时候，该账户似乎也引起了 Meta 版主的注意。据<a data-i13n="cpos:10;pos:1" href="https://twitter.com/eightiethmnt/status/1677322546792783872">Engadget 校友 Saqib Shah</a>称，Meta“错误地”从 Threads 中删除了该帐户。该公司短暂恢复了@elonmusksjet，然后再次暂停。</p><p>斯威尼曾经在推特上以@elonjet的名义发布飞机的航班信息，这在马斯克收购该公司之前很久就困扰了他。有一次，马斯克向斯威尼提出 5000 美元删除账户的提议，但遭到拒绝。 <a data-i13n="cpos:11;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/elon-musk-elonjet-twitter-bot-221826608.html">还价 50,000 美元</a>或在马斯克的一家公司实习的机会从未成功。</p><p>去年 12 月，也就是马斯克收购 Twitter 几个月后，该公司<a data-i13n="cpos:12;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/twitter-elonjet-banned-suspended-elon-musk-private-jet-153132962.html">永久暂停了</a>ElonJet 账户。 Twitter大约在同一时间<a data-i13n="cpos:13;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/twitter-announces-new-rules-about-location-sharing-amid-elonjet-controversy-005013326.html">更新了其私人信息规则</a>，以限制用户在合理时间过后分享“公开的位置信息，以便个人不再面临人身伤害的风险”。</p><p>斯威尼创建了一个新的 Twitter 帐户，该<a data-i13n="cpos:14;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/jack-sweeney-brings-delayed-version-of-elon-jet-back-to-twitter-112158491.html">帐户延迟 24 小时显示马斯克飞机的位置</a>，根据调整后的政策，这是可以接受的。其他平台上的 ElonJet 帐户显示更多最新信息，包括 Facebook、Telegram、 <a data-i13n="cpos:15;pos:1" href="https://mastodon.social/@elonjet">Mastodon</a>和<a data-i13n="cpos:16;pos:1" href="https://www.businessinsider.com/jack-dorsey-encourages-the-student-who-tracks-elon-musk-jet-2023-5">Bluesky</a> 。 <a data-i13n="cpos:17;pos:1" href="https://www.reddit.com/r/ElonJetTracker/">Reddit 的一个子版块</a>也在追踪这架飞机。</p><p> ElonJet 从未真正消失太久，但它出现在 Threads 上有一些非常合适的东西。这款新应用是 Twitter 的明目张胆的竞争对手。因此，Twitter 在指控<a data-i13n="cpos:18;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/twitter-threatens-to-sue-meta-over-the-new-threads-app-191141961.html">Meta 使用前员工和商业机密来开发 Threads 应用程序后，威胁要采取法律行动</a>。</p><p><strong>美国东部时间 7 月 7 日下午 3:51 更新：</strong> Meta 已在 Instagram 和 Threads 上暂停 @elonmusksjet。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/elonjet-is-now-posting-elon-musks-assassination-coordinates-on-twitter-rival-threads-164026053.html?src=rss]] >; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/elonjet-is-now-posting-elon-musks-assassination-coordinates-on-twitter-rival-threads-164026053.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> cd8450b3-f0ae-4b49-abbd-72c5ce57be31</guid><dc:creator>克里斯·霍尔特</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Fri, 07 Jul 2023 16:40:26 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1688760038</ingested><modified> 2023-07-07T20:00:43+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Media]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Kris Holt]]></category><media:content height="3000" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-07/ff8592a0-1ce0-11ee-97bb-7fd70085b782" width="4500"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="3000" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-07/ff8592a0-1ce0-11ee-97bb-7fd70085b782" width="4500"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Maxiphoto via Getty Images]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Commercial airplane icon locked on a radar simulation with gr